SIMPLE: underlying
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: underlying
<hw>un`der*ly"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Lying under or beneath; <as>as, the <ex>underlying</ex> strata of a
locality.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <def>Fundamental; basic; <as>as,
<ex>underlying</ex> principles; <ex>underlying</ex>
causes.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Implicit; not immediately obvious; requiring careful
scrutiny to discover; <as>as, the <ex>underlying</ex> sarcasm in her
seemingly innocuous remark.</as>.</def> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undermanned</ent>⟦br⟧
